<detall><id label=""><![CDATA[102133]]></id><title label="Titol"><![CDATA[2nd Eurofitness charity race]]></title><excerpt label="Resum"><![CDATA[<strong>Race.</strong> the Eurofitness 2014 cooperates with research in curing spinal injuries.]]></excerpt><content label="Contingut"><![CDATA[<p>The Eurofitness 2014 race will be held in conjunction with Fundació Fenexy, an organisation that is dedicated to curing spinal injuries. Most of the funds raised by this race will go to financing the project &#8216;Volver a Caminar&#8217; (Being Able to Walk Again), a research initiative aimed at curing injuries of this type.</p>
<p>The objective of &#8216;Volver a Caminar&#8217; is to allow recovery from spinal injuries through the combintion of multiple therapies. This interdisciplinary standpoint is what makes this project unique, and for that reason famous scientists from all around the world are taking part in it. The Eurofitness motto this year is &#8216;Córrer perquè tornin a córrer (Run so that they can run again)&#8217;.</p>
